verbose_text: Such OCM mediated TAK1 activation was considerably more apparent in 3bL8O17 cells, as evidenced by higher expression levels of p-TAK1 (Ser412) and p-IkappaBalpha (Ser32) when compared with those in 3bU2S8 cells, suggesting that TAK1 / NFkappaB activity was differentially regulated in metastatic cells and primary tumor cells upon OCM treatment.
